OL,3,CMuslim pilgrims warned over fake Hajj
OL,4,Ctravel packages
OL,6,FWith many UK Muslims preparing for the
OL,7,Fannual pilgrimage to Hajj in Saudi
OL,8,FArabia, Birmingham Trading Standards
OL,9,Fis warning residents to remain
OL,10,Fvigilant against Hajj fraud.
OL,12,FPeople are being advised to be alert
OL,13,Fto fake or suspiciously low-cost
OL,14,Fpackages and rogue travel agents.
OL,16,FHajj is one of the five pillars of
OL,17,FIslam and is a once-in-a-lifetime
OL,18,Fspiritual journey for many, making
OL,19,Fvictims particularly vulnerable to
OL,20,Fscams involving life savings.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
